{"h21a238b2g140dg4347g97efgc73583e61f8e": ["*Moan.*", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "d0f91371-87ab-1cb9-70dd-c6a7d8d80b9a"], "h25e7b8d9g1e69g4b6dg9f5dg539f72f83f95": ["He's back! You brought him back!", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "0eb53897-c8ff-fd7d-edff-37db415cd488"], "h2a514372g6d0ag4ac0ga9eegf0720c857a11": ["He's gone... you were right, he's gone. His scent is growing fainter.", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "c05e9f5c-2b92-58b8-82f6-b4080d1f8672"], "h7fea16b0g652fg4123g88d6g7d3832608140": ["Still nothing... still nothing...", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "58600f35-fb53-654d-db86-17547da2c715"], "hc2d208f1g418eg481ag9565g53c95fc0f565": ["He didn't come back, did he? His smell is gone. He's gone...", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "01161b92-f0d1-a825-30cd-2b08e863a4a9"], "h487083b2g796ag48d4ga25egc5ac0eaed341": ["Who are you looking for?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "c2f0d419-8ee6-8a52-3992-d87edfe7bf3c"], "h74889856ga8afg494agb49dga467a2535f0e": ["Master. He left with the weaponed two-legs. He said he'd be back.", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "e13c1947-b188-16a3-978d-dccaba8ff13d"], "hc0bbfe1eg70f1g463eg8eebgda293bffbe71": ["But I can smell them - the weaponed ones. And I cannot smell him... he's not coming back...", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "7ee47c84-0d1b-debe-43dd-1c64aff36210"], "h17b4cff2g2e3cg4e6egb3c0g314638a1e266": ["Don't worry - he'll be back.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "e0dd5773-239a-ba47-129c-923451a38ba8"], "heb9a4ffeg04e3g4a4eg9b9cgcc3ebb125fb7": ["No... the woods have gone dark. There's too many predators lately - even for Master.", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "785f8b8a-b9fa-a614-a209-4cfa8023e596"], "ha96d3570g0d22g4159g81c6g6ee50c6add21": ["You look strong. Why not go after him?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "521c0401-3773-741e-fe31-9b527ea39cd5"], "h597bbc84gfde8g47abga0b6ga21dfe0646d7": ["No... the woods have gone dark. There's too many predators lately - and I was never the strong one.", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "c155ddd8-f5c8-b36a-3dfd-0d22e052b005"], "h8ea57c5eg79b5g4500g9e85gb297f1a51825": ["Sounds like he's dead.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "5991c279-a384-8d4b-e965-0d0136c2a968"], "h67bcf094g7096g41c2gbdbbg13c0e1951920": ["No... it can't be! He wouldn't. Even... even with all the monsters...", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "06ae3927-8f3a-91bf-30b3-bd3a0d5f85a7"], "h2665c5a6gd98fg4968g8707g087500c553a0": ["*The bear whines, lonely and afraid.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "b5abe37e-0b97-a7fe-7dae-dc6344e7c2f5"], "h61cffa95gd782g4902g8c5bg771ff52d29f7": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "42b073da-ea00-fba7-d739-1c35f17b235d"], "h0cb0772bg2a3eg46e6ga0e1gd82ebfe32c74": ["You're the saddest bear I've ever seen. This is depressing.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "f1fcda8c-20de-3208-bb0f-f7a4291ba447"], "ha6b430aeg9229g4722ga47cga6a929a170e9": ["...Then leave.", "d4d4bfd2-9639-45bc-a256-2f079e53db29", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_WeepingTree_Bear.html", "a146a6f1-efd2-e33b-b03b-3a8052af3e36"]}